{"tid":1480913,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"睇天氣之子睇到喊咗","createTime":"2019-08-17T13:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:11:20.000Z","uid":110517,"like":115,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"3c3a3ce5c23626341957831b74b65a1620d08990","tid":1480913,"uid":110517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KYV1GOQdi4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKYV1GOQdi4s&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmhZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=bf96ed4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KYV1GOQdi4s</a><br />\n<br />\n你給予我的這份勇氣 只想為了你而使用<br />\n這份與你一起培育的愛 如果不是你就毫無意義了<br />\n我還能為我們的愛做些什麼<br />\n我還能為你做些什麼<br />\n為何要讓一無所有的我們看見夢想呢<br />\n為何要在有限的人生裡讓我們看到希望啊<br />\n為何總是賜給我們一些抓不住的東西<br />\n但仍想緊緊抓著它的我們 <br />\n是否很醜陋 還是說 很美呢？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong>"},{"pid":"9ea714fbcb56036cafed3be944b6f061de820ce9","tid":1480913,"uid":110517,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qQ8RymfAOZ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqQ8RymfAOZ0&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmhZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=1f1df878\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qQ8RymfAOZ0</a><br />\n可能係我地諗多咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1b137920a10f5830cb82c2d8096aac78ccba18","tid":1480913,"uid":289857,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:33:18.000Z","msg":"首大丈夫都好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歌詞又係應景<br />\n另外祝祭都好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/home/creationDetail.php?sn=4467307\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fhome%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D4467307&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmhZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=afd23d79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/home/creationDetail.php?sn=4467307</a> <br />\n<br />\n世界が君の小さな肩に　乗っているのが<br />\n只有我能看見你那小小的肩膀上<br />\n<br />\n僕にだけは見えて　泣き出しそうでいると<br />\n承載著世界　令我不禁感到眼眶泛淚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「大丈夫?」ってさぁ　君が気付いてさ　聞くから<br />\n「沒事吧？」　你察覺到後　於是問了我<br />\n<br />\n「大丈夫だよ」って　僕は慌てて言うけど<br />\n「沒事哦」　我慌張地回應著<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nなんでそんなことを　言うんだよ<br />\n為什麼要說那種話呢<br />\n<br />\n崩れそうなのは　君なのに<br />\n明明就快崩潰撐不下去的人是你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n取るに足らない　小さな僕の　有り余る今の　大きな夢は<br />\n微不足道又渺小的我　如今卻擁有如此宏大的夢想<br />\n<br />\n君の「大丈夫」になりたい　「大丈夫」になりたい<br />\n想要成為你的依靠　成為讓你安心的依靠<br />\n<br />\n君を大丈夫にしたいんじゃない　君にとっての　「大丈夫」になりたい<br />\n我不僅想讓你覺得可靠　更要成為你獨一無二的依靠"},{"pid":"db3e9b7cad87c78d502e64bc7448d5d0baafca4c","tid":1480913,"uid":121255,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"世界從來都是瘋狂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94d9ffa8aa52d3331f81eb76d718a951246d5d6","tid":1480913,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"未睇 可能都唔得閒睇<br />\n唉無心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7c8de93202e58cd3ab7c0738dedc3b187d97a3","tid":1480913,"uid":261013,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:41:02.000Z","msg":"我睇睇下真係喊咗出嚟<br />\n而且係唔自覺咁樣流眼淚"},{"pid":"2a4747bd5f783419526457476e044a435ff41025","tid":1480913,"uid":110517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9b7c8de93202e58cd3ab7c0738dedc3b187d97a3","tid":1480913,"uid":261013,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:41:02.000Z","msg":"我睇睇下真係喊咗出嚟<br />\n而且係唔自覺咁樣流眼淚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:42:10.000Z","msg":"我都係 本身都唔係一個眼淺嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae203153b23fee8d38dca593d187db48ccdddaf","tid":1480913,"uid":110517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c94d9ffa8aa52d3331f81eb76d718a951246d5d6","tid":1480913,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"未睇 可能都唔得閒睇<br />\n唉無心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:43:11.000Z","msg":"明嘅 聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2403db9641a60dcae080537051851035e7819b","tid":1480913,"uid":187626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:43:57.000Z","msg":"由世界繼續癲狂吧"},{"pid":"e8389096d6bd3fee107c059e1866c5d98774ac65","tid":1480913,"uid":110517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db3e9b7cad87c78d502e64bc7448d5d0baafca4c","tid":1480913,"uid":121255,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"世界從來都是瘋狂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"They don&rsquo;t know and they don&rsquo;t care<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c5be3b423a4e01197f19fecf9b4c20b84005bc","tid":1480913,"uid":272652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:45:31.000Z","msg":"全部歌都好正，配樂又正，大丈夫正過宣傳片首主題曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459898ad8f483d9eb268c4d6df627e624c6a114c","tid":1480913,"uid":58453,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"4d1b137920a10f5830cb82c2d8096aac78ccba18","tid":1480913,"uid":289857,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:33:18.000Z","msg":"首大丈夫都好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 